{"tid":1846493,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"禮賓府旁有間廢置醫院，適合做隔離中心。","createTime":"2020-01-27T15:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T15:43:24.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"228d9bdf5df51b386dc8dc51b820252a7096f50a","tid":1846493,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"禮賓府旁有間廢置醫院，適合做隔離中心。<br />\n<br />\n港中醫院廢置8年，保存良好，地點人口密度低，遠離主要民居，亦非主要幹道，環境清幽適合養病。<br />\n<br />\n最重要是，由禮賓府步行至醫院，僅1分鐘路程，方便特首探望武肺病人及隨時入住。<br />\n<br />\n醫院屬聖公會物業，而聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴又同政府關係極之良好，絕對有得傾，強烈建議改成隔離中心。<br />\n<br />\n轉facebook-家明<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kaminghk/photos/177203753628830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkaminghk%2Fphotos%2F177203753628830&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=25444dd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kaminghk/photos/177203753628830</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推  救救同胞🙇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1NvKo6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1NvKo6.jpg&h=3cffaf2b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}